For data bound controls:
- DataBindings property on GUI controls - bind any property of the control with a property of the object
- Binding class - (propName, dataSource, dataMember)


DataSet
- initially it is empty
- typed/untyped

SqlDataAdapter - Update(), Fill()
Update() - check the RowState ({Added, Modified, Deleted, Detached, Unchanged})
- execute the corresponding command (InsertCommand, DeleteCommand, UpdateCommand)
- Fill() using the SelectCommand tot retrieve data from the data source

DataRelation: 
- GetChildRows()
- GetParentRow()
- ForeignKeyConstraint automatically added

Constraints:
ForeignKeyConstraint, Unique Constraint
DataTable.Constraints
DataSet.EnforceConstraints = true (default)

Entity Framework - ADO.NET technologies to support data-oriented apps
- enables devs to work with domain specific objects and queries (LINQ) and the framework automatically translates them to data source specific language
